lead_paragraph: The winner of the 2015 Miss America Pageant will be crowned on Sunday night in Atlantic City, and the wearer's glittering tiara will stand in contrast to the tarnished fortunes of this New Jersey beach town where yet another casino is slated to close this week.

headline.main: Miss America to Be Crowned Sunday in Stressed Atlantic City, N.J.
